          description: "Delicate buttery shortcrust cups filled with a rich, silky vanilla bean pastry cream, crowned with vibrant raw strawberries and a glistening apricot glaze.",
          culturalNote: "The Tartelette aux Fraises is a quintessential hallmark of traditional French patisserie. Its brilliance lies in the harmony of sensory contrasts: the crisp, buttery snap of the shortcrust shell, the luscious vanilla comfort of the creme patissiere, and the bright, acidic burst of fresh raw strawberries on top.",
